      "name": "Bench-level hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA benchmark centrifugal pump study across five operating points. Agreement within 15% at all operating conditions.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/act-cfd-validation-run-2024",
