    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) provides a conservative regulatory margin. Assessment accepted for submission.",
